comment: Greetings from the Netherlands!! I always love your content. I was watching netflix and recognized you again! It was cool to know one of my favorite korean youtubers on a deeper level by netflix. We all handle relationships differently based on our life experiences, it always mirrors our insecurities and challenges.  From a western perspective, you handled all the relationship challenges head on, full respect for the both of you!!. Also Jiyu deserves more likes and views, don't you all think that?! (in addition, i always appreciate the english subsss <><><>)
